              <span class="st-tag">Pain</span>
              <p>Agents are deployed without a trusted context layer; AI retrieves documents but doesn't understand company meaning; governance and audit are urgent.</p>
              <span class="st-tag h">Message</span>
              <p>Orient gives agents the organisation's meaning, not just its documents.</p>
