          <h2>Price as a high-value organisational intelligence layer.</h2>
          <p>Not a lightweight collaboration tool. <b>Orient for Humans:</b> tiered seat pricing — $36 per full user (Team) and $55 (Organisation, including the meaning-layer base); viewers free. <b>Orient for Machines:</b> priced as infrastructure — platform fee, machine consumer fee, meaning consumption.</p>
          <span class="st-tag m">Machine platform ranges</span>
          <ul class="m">
            <li>Machine Starter: $12k–$30k ARR;</li>
            <li>Machine Team: $60k–$120k ARR;</li>
            <li>Machine Enterprise: $300k+ ARR;</li>
            <li>Strategic Infrastructure: $500k+ ARR.</li>
          </ul>
          <span class="st-tag">Account value examples</span>
          <div class="st-table-wrap">
