          <h2>Start with AI-native and software companies.</h2>
          <p>The first beachhead: <b>AI-native and software companies with complex knowledge, active strategic work, and a near-term need for agents.</b> They understand the agent problem, move quickly, have complex internal knowledge, need strategy/product/sales/investor narratives, are likely to adopt both products, and can become reference customers.</p>
